						<summary>

						<p>This is badly damaged. It seems to record a gift of 15 <hi rend="italic">Varāhaṉ</hi> for the several requirements of worship and offerings in the temple. The amount was deposited with the <hi rend="italic">Śivabrāhmaṇas</hi> who undertook to manage the affairs. The donor's name is lost.</p>						

